        <heading>123.  Form of award; effect of remarriage or death</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 123.  Form of award; effect of remarriage or death
The sum awarded for contributions made to the education or training of a spouse may be a sum certain payable in installments.
The award shall not terminate upon the remarriage or death of either party.</p>
        </content>
